  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 3 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Father of 3 children killed in firing!",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A firing incident has been reported in Ambalangodai - Palapitiya, Urawatha area itself.",
        "The police said that a 30-year-old father of 3 children died in this shooting.",
        "The police are conducting further investigations as the information about the reason for the murder is not known.",
        "It is to be noted that the said person is a suspect in a murder case and that the gun was used on his way back from the court."
      ],
